msgid "Highlights"
msgstr "亮点"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:9
msgid ""
"C8(INT8 KV cache) is now supported for GQA attention models, and also "
"supported on DeepSeek-V3.1 with PD disaggregation scenario. "
"[#7474](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7474), "
"[#7222](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7222)"
msgstr ""
"C8（INT8 KV 缓存）现已支持 GQA 注意力模型，并且在 PD 解耦场景下的 DeepSeek-V3.1 中也得到支持。"
"[#7474](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7474), "
"[#7222](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7222)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:10
msgid ""
"DeepSeek models are now supported on A5 through new MLA operators. "
"[#7232](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7232)"
msgstr ""
"通过新的 MLA 算子，DeepSeek 模型现已在 A5 上得到支持。"
"[#7232](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7232)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:12
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:54
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:107
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:200
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:307
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:402
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:448
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:505
msgid "Features"
msgstr "功能"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:14
msgid ""
"Flash Comm V1 now supports VL models with MLA, removing a previous "
"limitation for multimodal serving. [#7390](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/pull/7390)"
msgstr ""
"Flash Comm V1 现已支持使用 MLA 的 VL 模型，移除了之前对多模态服务的一个限制。"
"[#7390](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7390)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:15
msgid ""
"Support separate attention backends for target and draft models in "
"speculative decoding, allowing finer backend tuning per model. "
"[#7342](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7342)"
msgstr ""
"支持在推测式解码中为目标模型和草稿模型使用独立的注意力后端，允许针对每个模型进行更精细的后端调优。"
"[#7342](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7342)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:16
msgid ""
"VL MoE models now support SP, and `sp_threshold` is removed in favor of "
"`sp_min_token_num` from vLLM. [#7044](https://github.com/vllm-project"
"/vllm-ascend/pull/7044)"
msgstr ""
"VL MoE 模型现在支持 SP，并且移除了 `sp_threshold`，转而采用 vLLM 的 `sp_min_token_num`。"
"[#7044](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7044)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:17
msgid ""
"Qwen VL models now support `w8a8_mxfp8` quantization. "
"[#7417](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7417)"
msgstr ""
"Qwen VL 模型现在支持 `w8a8_mxfp8` 量化。"
"[#7417](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7417)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:19
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:66
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:124
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:228
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:327
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:408
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:463
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:515
msgid "Performance"
msgstr "性能"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:21
msgid ""
"Optimized Triton operator recompilation to reduce redundant rebuilds and "
"unnecessary recompilation triggered by function parameter optimization. "
"[#7647](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7647) "
"[#7645](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7645)"
msgstr ""
"优化了 Triton 算子的重编译，以减少由函数参数优化触发的冗余重建和不必要的重新编译。"
"[#7647](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7647) "
"[#7645](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7645)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:22
msgid ""
"Optimized the Qwen3.5 and Qwen3-Next GDN prefill path by prebuilding "
"chunk metadata, reducing host-device synchronization overhead. "
"[#7487](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7487)"
msgstr ""
"通过预构建分块元数据，优化了 Qwen3.5 和 Qwen3-Next GDN 的预填充路径，减少了主机-设备同步开销。"
"[#7487](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7487)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:23
msgid ""
"Simplified the FIA prefill context merge path for better runtime "
"efficiency. [#7293](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/7293)"
msgstr ""
"简化了 FIA 预填充上下文合并路径，以提高运行时效率。"
"[#7293](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7293)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:25
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:73
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:142
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:250
#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:367
msgid "Documentation"
