#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:27
msgid ""
"Refreshed deployment and model docs for Kimi-K2.5, GLM-4.7, "
"DeepSeek-V3.2, MiniMax-M2.5, and PD disaggregation guides. "
"[#7371](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7371) "
"[#7403](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7403) "
"[#7292](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7292) "
"[#7296](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7296) "
"[#7300](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7300)"
msgstr ""
"更新了 Kimi-K2.5、GLM-4.7、DeepSeek-V3.2、MiniMax-M2.5 的部署和模型文档，以及 PD 解耦指南。"
"[#7371](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7371) "
"[#7403](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7403) "
"[#7292](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7292) "
"[#7296](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7296) "
"[#7300](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7300)"

