#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:95
msgid ""
"In hybrid models, the minimum token count required for a prefix cache hit"
" is currently large. The exact number is related to tp size, e.g., with "
"tp 2, the block_size is adjusted to 2048, which means that any prefix "
"shorter than 2048 will never be cached."
msgstr "在混合模型中，当前前缀缓存命中所需的最小令牌数较大。具体数值与 TP 大小相关，例如，当 TP=2 时，block_size 调整为 2048，这意味着任何短于 2048 的前缀都不会被缓存。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:96
msgid ""
