"inference may hang when concurrency exceeds 8 (fixed in PR "
"[#7235](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7235) "
"[#7290](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7290))."
msgstr "GLM5 在 2 节点 PD 混合部署场景中存在一个问题：当并发数超过 8 时，推理可能会挂起（已在 PR [#7235](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7235) 和 [#7290](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7290) 中修复）。"

