"please apply the changes from the upstream `vllm-project/vllm` "
"repository, specifically from pull requests [#33320](https://github.com"
"/vllm-project/vllm/pull/33320) and [#34501](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm/pull/34501). [#6755](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/6755)"
msgstr ""
