"ascend/pull/6204)"
msgstr ""
"**多模态**：在 AscendMMEncoderAttention 中并行化 Q/K/V 填充以获得更好的性能。[#6204](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/6204)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:347
msgid ""
"**CANN**: Upgraded to 8.5.0 [#6112](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/6112)"
msgstr ""
