msgstr ""
"**torch-npu**：已升级至 2.8.0.post2。默认安装在 Docker 容器中。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:349
msgid ""
"**triton-ascend**: Upgraded to 3.2.0 [#6105](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/pull/6105)"
msgstr ""
"**triton-ascend**：已升级至 3.2.0 [#6105](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/6105)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:350
msgid ""
"**vLLM**: Upgraded to 0.13.0 and dropped 0.12.0 support. "
"[#5146](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/5146)"
msgstr ""
