"**Transformers**：已升级至 >= 4.57.4 [#5250](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/5250)"

#: ../../source/user_guide/release_notes.md:355
msgid ""
"**CPUOffloadingConnector** is deprecated. We'll remove it in the next "
